name: Kelly Smith
description: I am a very fun loving man. I work hard, but I can play hard too. I am self employed and financially and emotionally secure. I have been told by my friends that I am attractive, witty, fun to be with, well, you get the idea. I like to cook, grill out and dine out. I’m a true easy going hopeful romantic that can’t wait for that special woman to pamper.
